                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1607472586893-edb57cb641ce?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Fuga de agua" class="object-cover w-full h-full opacity-80 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500">
